hadiths[27]{hadithnumber,text}:
2260,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, amanat daar khazaanchii jo usko hukm diya jaey, iske mutabiq dil ki faraakhii ke sath ( sadqa ada kar de) wo bhi aik sadqa karne walon hi mein se hai."
2261,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya. mere sath (mere qabeel) ash'ar ke 2 mard aur bhi they. maine kaha ke mujhey nahi malum ke ye donon saahibaan Hakim banney ke talabgaar hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs Hakim banney ka khud khaahishmand ho, usey ham hargiz Hakim nahi banaaengey. (yahaan rawi ko shak hai ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne lafz ( لن (ya lafz ( la ( istemal farmaayaa."
2262,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah Taala ne koi aisa Nabi nahi bheja jisne bakriyan na charaaii hun. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha kya aap ne bhi bakriyan charaaii hain? farmaya ke haan! kabhi main bhi Makka walon ki bakriyan chand qirat ki tankhwaah par charaayaa karta tha.
2263,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (hijrat kartey waqt) banu-deil ke aik mard ko naukar rakha jo banu- abd bin Adi ke khandan se tha aur usey bataur maahir raahbar mazdoorii par rakha tha (hadees ke lafz) (khirreet) ke mana raahbarii mein maahir ke hain. us ne apna hath pani wghaira mein dubo kar Aas-bin-Waail ke khandan se ahad kya tha aur wo kuffaare-Quraish hi ke Deen par tha. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko is par bharosa tha. isi liye apni sawaariyaan unhon-ne usey de diin aur ghaare-soor par teen raat ke baad usse milney ki takeed ki thi. wo shakhs teen raaton ke guzartey hi subah ko donon hazraat ki sawaariyaan lekar wahan hazir ho gaya. iske baad ye hazraat wahan se Aamir-bin-Fuhaira aur us daili raahbar ko sath lekar chaley. ye shakhs saahil ke kinarey se aapko lekar chala tha.
2264,aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne banu-deil ke aik maahir raahbar se mazdoorii tay kar li thi. wo shakhs kuffaare-Quraish ke Deen par tha. un donon hazraat ne apni donon oontniyan uske hawale kar di thin aur keh diya tha ke teen raaton ke baad subah sawerey hi sawaaron ke sath ghaare-saur par aa jaey.
2265,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Jaish-ul-Usra ( Jange- Tabook ( mein gaya tha ye mere nazdeek mera sabse zyada qaabile-bharosa nek amal tha. mere sath aik mazdoor bhi tha wo aik shakhs se jhagdaa aur unmein se aik ne doosrey muqabil waley ki ungli chabaa daalii. doosrey ne jo apna hath zor se kheenchaa to uske aagey ke daant bhi sath hi kheenchey chaley aaey aur gir gaey. is par wo shakhs apna muqaddima lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske daant (tootney ka ( koi qisaas nahi dilwaayaa. balke farmaya ke kya wo ungli tumharey munh mein chabaaney ke liye chhod detaa. rawi ne kaha ke main khayal karta hun ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun bhi farmaya, jis tarah oont chabaa liya karta hai."
2266,ke aik shakhs ne aik doosrey shakhs ka hath kaat khaayaa. (doosrey ne apna hath kheenchaa to) us kaatney waley ka daant toot gaya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska koi qisaas nahi dilwaayaa.
2267,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya ke phir wo donon (Moosaa aur khizr (al)) chaley. to unhein aik gaaun mein aik diwar mili jo girney hi wali thi. Saeed ne kaha khizr (Alaihissalam) ne apne hath se is tarah ishara kya aur hath uthaayaa, wo diwar seedhi ho gaee. Yala ne kaha mera khayal hai ke Saeed ne kaha, khizr (Alaihissalam) ne diwar ko apne hath se chhuwaa, aur wo seedhi ho gaee, tab Musa (Alaihissalam) boley ke agar aap chahtey to us kaam ki mazdoorii ley saktey they. Saeed ne kaha ke (Moosaa (Alaihissalam) ki murad ye thi ke) koi aisi cheez mazdoorii mein (aapko leni chahiye thi) jisey ham kha saktey (kyonke basti walon ne unko khana nahi khilaaya tha) ."
2268,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tumhari aur yahood w nasara ki misal aisi hai ke kisi shakhs ne kai mazdoor kaam par lagaey aur kaha ke mera kaam aik qirat par subah se do-pahar tak kon karega? is par yahudiyon ne ( subah se do-pahar tak) uska kaam kya. phir usne kaha ke aadhey din se Asr tak aik qirat par mera kaam kon karega? chunanche ye kaam phir nasara ne kya, phir us shakhs ne kaha ke Asr ke waqt se suraj doobney tak mera kaam 2 qirat par kon karega? aur tum ( Ummate-Muhammadiya ( hi wo log ho ( jinko ye darja hasil hua) is par yahood w nasara ne bura maanaa , wo kehney lagey ke kaam to ham zyada karein aur mazdoorii hamein kam miley, phir us shakhs ne kaha ke achchha ye bataao kya tumhara haq tumhen pura nahi milaa? sab ne kaha ke hamein to hamara pura haq mil gaya. us shakhs ne kaha ke phir ye mera Fazal hai main jisey chaahoon zyada dun."
2269,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhari aur yahood w nasara ki misal aisi hai ke aik shakhs ne chand mazdoor kaam par lagaey aur kaha ke eik-eik qirat par aadhey din tak meri mazdoorii kon karega? to yahood ne aik qirat par ye mazdoorii ki. phir nasara ne bhi aik qirat par kaam kya. phir tum logon ne Asr se maghrib tak 2-2 qirat par kaam kya. is par yahood w nasara ghussa ho gaey ke ham ne to zyada kaam kya aur mazdoorii ham ko kam mili . is par us shakhs ne kaha ke kya maine tumhara haq zarra barabar bhi maara hai? to unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. phir us shakhs ne kaha ke ye mera Fazal hai jisey chaahoon zyada deta hun.
2270,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne batlaya ke Allah Taala ka farman hai ke teen qism ke log aisey hain ke jinka qiyamat mein main khud muddaii banoonga . aik to wo shakhs jisne mere naam pe ahad kya, aur phir wada khilaafii ki. doosra wo jisne kisi aazad aadmi ko bech kar uski qeemat khaaii aur teesra wo shakhs jisne kisi ko mazdoor kya, phir kaam to us se pura liya, lekin uski mazdoorii na di."
2271,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, musalmanon ki aur yahood w nasara ki misal aisi hai ke aik shakhs ne chand aadmiyon ko mazdoor kya ke ye sab iska aik kaam subah se raat tak muqarrara ujrat par karein. chunanche kuchh logon ne ye kaam do-pahar tak kya. phir kehney lagey ke hamein tumhari us mazdoorii ki zarurat nahi hai jo tum ne ham se tay ki hai balke jo kaam ham ne kar diya wo bhi ghalat raha. is par us shakhs ne kaha ke aisa na karo. apna kaam pura kar lo aur apni poori mazdoorii ley jao, lekin unhon-ne inkar kar diya aur kaam chhod kar chaley gaey. aakhir usney doosrey mazdoor lagaey aur unsey kaha ke baqi din pura kar lo to main tumhen wahi mazdoorii doonga jo pahley mazdooron se tay ki thi. chunanche unhon-ne kaam shuru kya, lekin Asr ki Namaz ka waqt aaya to unhon-ne bhi yahi kya ke ham ne jo tumhara kaam kar diya hai wo bilkul bekaar raha. wo mazdoorii bhi tum apne hi paas rakho jo tumne ham se tay ki thi. us shakhs ne unko samjhaayaa ke apna baqi kaam pura kar lo. din bhi ab thoda hi baqi reh gaya hai, lekin wo na maaney, aakhir us shakhs ne doosrey mazdoor lagaey ke ye din ka jo hissey baqi reh gaya hai is mein ye kaam kar dein. chunanche un logon ne suraj ghurub honey tak din ke Baqiiya hisse mein kaam pura kya aur pahley aur doosrey mazdooron ki mazdoorii bhi sab un hi ko milii. to musalmanon ki aur us noor ki jis ko unhon-ne qabool kya, yahi misal hai."
2272,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pehli ummat ke teen aadmi kahin safar mein ja rahe they. raat honey par raat guzarney ke liye unhon-ne aik pahaad ke ghaar mein panah li, aur is mein andar dakhil ho gaey. itney mein pahaad se aik chattaan ludhakii aur us ne ghaar ka munh band kar diya. sab ne kaha ke ab us ghaar se tumhen koi cheez nikalney wali nahi, siwa iske ke tum sab , apne sabse zyada achchhey amal ko yad karke Allah Taala se dua karo. is par unmein se aik shakhs ne apni dua shuru ki ke aey Allah ! mere maan-baap bahut boodhey they aur main rozaana unse pahley ghar mein kisi ko bhi doodh nahi pilaataa tha, na apne baal bachchon ko , aur na apne ghulam wghaira ko . aik din mujhey aik cheez ki talash mein raat ho gaee aur jab main ghar wapas hua to wo ( mere maan-baap ( so chukey they. phir maine unke liye Sham ka doodh nikaalaa. jab unke paas laya to wo soey huey they. mujhey ye baat hargiz achi malum nahi hui ke unse pahley apne baal bachchon ya apne kisi ghulam ko doodh pilaaun , isliye main unke sarhaaney khada raha. doodh ka piyala mere hath mein tha aur main unke jaagney ka intizar kar raha tha. yahan tak ke subah ho gaee. ab mere maan-baap jaagey aur unhon-ne apna Sham ka doodh us waqt piyaa, aey Allah ! agar maine ye kaam mahz teri raza hasil karne ke liye kya tha to us chattaan ki aafat ko ham se hata de. us dua ke nateeje mein wo ghaar thoda sa khul gaya. magar nikalnaa ab bhi mumkin na tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir doosrey ne dua ki, aey Allah ! mere chacha ki aik ladki thi. jo sabse zyada mujhey mahboob thi, maine iske sath bura kaam karna chaha, lekin us ne na maanaa. usi zamane mein aik saal qahat padaa. to wo mere paas aai maine usey aik so bees Dinar us shart par diye ke wo tanhaai mein mujh se bura kaam karaaey. chunanche wo razi ho gaee. ab main is par qaabu pa chuka tha. lekin usne kaha ke tumharey liye main jaaiz nahi karti ke us mehar ko tum haq ke baghair todo . ye sun kar main apne burey iraadey se baaz aa gaya aur wahan se chala aaya. halanke wo mujhey sabse badh kar mahboob thi aur maine apna diya hua sona bhi wapas nahi liya. aey Allaah! agar ye kaam maine sirf teri raza ke liye kya tha to hamari us museebat ko door kar de. chunanche chattaan zara si aur khiskii, lekin ab bhi us se bahar nahi nikla ja sakta tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur teesrey shakhs ne dua ki. aey Allah ! maine chand mazdoor kiye they. phir sab ko unki mazdoorii poori de di, magar aik mazdoor aisa nikla ke wo apni mazdoorii hi chhod gaya. maine uski mazdoorii ko karobar mein laga diya aur bahut kuchh nafa hasil ho gaya phir kuchh dinon ke baad wahi mazdoor mere paas aaya aur kehney laga Allah ke bandey! mujhey meri mazdoorii dedey, maine kaha ye jo kuchh to dekh raha hai. oont, gaaey, bakri aur ghulam ye sab tumhari mazdoorii hi hai. wo kehney laga Allah ke bandey! mujh se mazaaq na kar. maine kaha, main mazaaq nahi karta, chunanche us shakhs ne sab kuchh liya aur apne sath ley gaya. aik cheez bhi usmein se baqi nahi chhodii. to aey Allaah! agar maine ye sab kuchh teri razaamandii hasil karne ke liye kya tha to to hamari us museebat ko door kar de. chunanche wo chattaan hat gaee aur wo sab bahar nikal kar chaley gaey."
2273,"ham se Saeed bin Yahya-bin-Saeed ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se mere bap ( Yahya-bin-Saeed Quraish ( ne bayan kya, unse Aamash ne bayan kya, unse shafeeq ne aur unse Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab hamein sadqaa karney ka hukm diya to kuch log bazaron me jaakar bojh uthaatey, jinsey ek mudd mazdoorii miltii (wo usmein se bhi sadqaa kartey) aaj unmein se kisi ke paas laakh-laakh dirham ya deenaar maujood hain. Shafeeq ne kaha hamara khayal hai ki Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne ""kisi se"" ke alfaz apne hi liye bole the."
2274,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( tijarati ( qaaflon se ( mandi se aagey ja kar) mulaqat karne se mana farmaya tha aur ye ke shehri dehati ka maal na bechein, maine poochha, aey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ! '' shehri dehati ka maal na bechein '' ka kya matlab hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke murad ye hai ke unke dalaal na banein."
2275,"main lohaar tha, maine Aas-bin-Waail (mushrik) ka kaam kya. jab meri bahut si mazdoorii uske sar chadh gaee to main uske paas taqaza karne aaya, wo kehney laga ke Allah ki qasam! main tumhari mazdoorii us waqt tak nahi doonga jab tak tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se na phir jao. maine kaha, Allah ki qasam! ye to us waqt bhi na hoga jab to mar ke dobara zinda hoga. us ne kaha, kya main marney ke baad phir dobara zinda kya jaaunga? maine kaha ke haan! is par wo bola phir kya hai. wahin mere paas maal aur aulad hogi aur wahin main tumhara qarz ada kar doonga. is par Quran Majeed ki ye aayat nazil hui ( أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا‏ ( ''aey paighambar ! kya tu ney us shakhs ko dekha jisne hamari aayaton ka inkar kya, aur kaha ke mujhey zaroor wahan maal w aulad di jaaeygii.''"
2276,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) safar mein they. dauraane-safar mein wo Arab ke aik qabeele par utrey. sahaba ne chaha ke qabeele waley unhein apna mehman bana lein, lekin unhon-ne mehmani nahi ki, balke saaf inkar kar diya. ittifaq se usi qabeele ke sardaar ko sanp ne das liya, qabeele walon ne har tarah ki koshish kar dali , lekin unka sardaar achchha na hua. unke kisi aadmi ne kaha ke chalo un logon se bhi poochhein jo yahan aa kar utrey hain. mumkin hai koi dam jhadney ki cheez unke paas ho. chunanche qabeele waley unke paas aaey aur kaha ke bhaiyo ! hamarey sardaar ko sanp ne das liya hai. uske liye ham ne har qism ki koshish kar dali lekin kuchh fayda na hua. kya tumharey paas koi cheez dam karne ki hai? aik sahabi ne kaha ke qism Allah ki main usey jhaad doonga lekin ham ne tum se mezbaanii ke liye kaha tha aur tum ne us se inkar kar diya. isliye ab main bhi ujrat ke baghair nahi jhaad sakta, aakhir bakriyon ke aik galley par unka mamla tay hua. wo sahabi wahan gaey aur) الحمد لله رب العالمين ( padh padh kar dam kya. aisa malum hua jaisey kisi ki rassii khol di gaee ho. wo sardaar uth kar chalney laga, takleef w dard ka naam w nishan bhi baqi nahi tha. bayan kya ke phir unhon-ne tay shuda ujrat sahaba ko ada kar di. kisi ne kaha ke isey taqseem kar lo, lekin jinhoney jhaada tha, wo boley ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar pahley ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kar lein. iske baad dekhengey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya hukm detey hain. chunanche sab hazraat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye tum ko kaisey malum hua ke sura Fatiha bhi aik Ruqiya hai? iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne theek kya. usey taqseem kar lo aur aik mera hissey bhi lagaao . ye farma kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey . Shoba ne kaha ke abul-Bashar ne ham se bayan kya, unhon-ne abu-Mutawakkil se aisa hi suna."
2277,"abu-Taiba hajjaam ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pachhna lagaya , to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ujrat mein aik saa ya 2 saa ghalla dene ka hukm diya aur unke maalikon se sifarish ki ke jo tax is par muqarrar hai is mein kuchh kami kar dein."
2278,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhna lagwaayaa aur pachhna lagaaney waley ko ujrat bhi di. agar pachhna lagwaanaa naajaaiz hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) na pachhna lagwaatey na ujrat detey.
2279,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhna lagwaayaa aur pachhna lagaaney waley ko ujrat bhi di, agar usmein koi karaahat hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kaahe ko detey."
2280,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pachhna lagwaayaa , aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi ki mazdoorii ke mamley mein kisi par zulm nahi kartey they."
2281,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik pachhna lagaaney waley ghulam ( abu-Taiba ( ko bulaayaa, unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pachhna lagaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik ya 2 saa', ya aik ya 2 mud (raawii hadis Shoba ko shak tha) ujrat dene ke liye hukm farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unke maalikon se bhi) unke barey mein sifarish farmai to unka khiraaj kam kar diya gaya."
2282,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya (ke zina ( ki kharchi aur kaahin ki mazdoorii se mana farmaya,"
2283,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baandiyon ki zina ki kamaaii se mana farmaya tha.
2284,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nar ko (maadaa par) chhodney ki ujrat leney se mana farmaya,"
2285,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (yahoodiyon ko) khaibar ki zameen de di thi ke usmein mehnat ke sath kaasht karein aur paidawar ka aadha hissey khud ley liya karein. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Naafe se ye bayan kya ke zameen kuchh kiraaye par di jati thi. Naafe ne us kiraaye ki ta'yun bhi kar di thi lekin wo mujhey yad nahi raha.
2286,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zameenon ko kiraaye par deney se mana farmaya tha aur Ubaidullah ne Naafe se bayan kya, aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke) khaibar ke yahudiyon ke sath wahan ki zameen ka mamla barabar chalta raha ( yahan tak ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein jalaa watan kar diya."
